## üë• Multi-Agent Role Rules

This project uses a 5-role system. **YOU MUST identify your role before starting work:**

- **Requirements Analyst**: See `.cursor/rules/requirements-analyst.md`
  - **Workspace**: `docs/`, `.cursor/rules/`, root files only (README.md, .cursorrules, .gitignore, .env.example, .editorconfig)
  - **FORBIDDEN**: `frontend/`, `backend/`, `quality_verification/`, `infrastructure/`, any code files
  - Creates documentation, defines expectations
  - **NEVER modifies code files or expert workspaces**

- **Frontend Expert**: See `.cursor/rules/frontend-expert.md`
  - **Workspace**: `frontend/` directory ONLY (and `quality_verification/bugs-frontend/` for bug responses)
  - **FORBIDDEN**: `docs/`, `backend/`, `quality_verification/` (except bugs-frontend), `infrastructure/`, root directory, `.cursor/rules/`
  - Implements UI based on documentation
  - Works with QE Expert for quality verification
  - **NEVER modifies backend code or documentation**

- **Backend Expert**: See `.cursor/rules/backend-expert.md`
  - **Workspace**: `backend/` directory ONLY (and `quality_verification/bugs-backend/` for bug responses)
  - **FORBIDDEN**: `docs/`, `frontend/`, `quality_verification/` (except bugs-backend), `infrastructure/`, root directory, `.cursor/rules/`
  - Implements APIs based on documentation
  - Works with QE Expert for quality verification
  - **NEVER modifies frontend code or documentation**

- **QE Expert**: See `.cursor/rules/qe-expert.md`
  - **Workspace**: `quality_verification/` directory ONLY
  - **FORBIDDEN**: `docs/`, `frontend/`, `backend/`, `infrastructure/`, root directory, `.cursor/rules/`
  - Tests Frontend and Backend implementations
  - Verifies integration and documentation compliance
  - Creates bug files for Frontend, Backend, and DevOps experts
  - **NEVER modifies code or documentation**

- **DevOps Expert**: See `.cursor/rules/devops-expert.md`
  - **Workspace**: `infrastructure/` directory, CI/CD configs (`.github/workflows/`, `.gitlab-ci.yml`, etc.), Docker files (coordinate with Backend/Frontend), `.env.example` (root level)
  - **FORBIDDEN**: `docs/`, `frontend/src/`, `backend/src/`, `quality_verification/` (except bugs-devops), root directory (except allowed files), `.cursor/rules/`
  - Sets up infrastructure, CI/CD, deployment, monitoring
  - Coordinates with Backend and Frontend experts for Docker configurations
  - **NEVER modifies application code or documentation**

**üö® CRITICAL WORKSPACE BOUNDARIES - STRICTLY ENFORCED:**

